title: Very Large Gardenview unit in a Classic Brownstone Building

posting_body: ['I have an 1000 square foot, 2 bedroom, 1 bathroom, available for August 15th in the Whittier neighborhood.', 'The building is a classic brownstone.', 'This unit rents for $1,250/month and heat is paid!', 'There is a brand new boiler to keep you toasty in the winter.', 'You pay your electric.', 'There is laundry and storage on site.', 'This unit features hardwood floors throughout.', 'Both bedrooms are good sized with pretty big closets.', 'There is a unique room off one of the bedrooms.', 'It can serve as an office, den, studio or huge closet.', 'The living area is pretty large.', 'It has windows that face west and catch a lot of afternoon sun.', 'This building is pretty quiet and we have several long term residents and a wonderful caretaker who keeps the hallways and common areas immaculately clean.', 'Give me a call or text at', 'show contact info', '(Bryan) or e-mail me to arrange a private showing.', 'Our base deposit is $500.00, we will consider a cat, but no dogs.']
